287,The stream-consumer Deployment operates in the ml namespace. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It requires running in a container named server. It includes pulling elasticsearch:14. It is configured with maintaining 5 pods.
288,Spin up an Ingress called model-trainer-ingress in the platform namespace. It should have responding to requests for example.com.
289,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name health-checker-config, deployed to monitoring."
290,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name payment-gateway-svc, deployed to logging. Specifications include configured as LoadBalancer."
291,"Please configure a Service identified as order-service-svc within ml. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Make sure it has carrying label tier: cache, operating on TCP, matching pods carrying app=load-balancer, with service type LoadBalancer."
292,"We need a Deployment named ml-inference in logging. The configuration requires naming the container ml-inference, while also pulling traefik:3.0, and with 2 replicas."
293,"We need a Service named cdn-origin-svc in ml. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. The configuration requires a node port of 31153, exposing port 5432, operating as a NodePort service, with the env label set to testing, while also forwarding to target port 8200."
294,"Set up an Ingress called rate-limiter-ingress in the default namespace. It should have accessible via port 80, routing /metrics requests, routing to backend service catalog-api-svc, with a Prefix pathType, and routing requests to api.example.com."
295,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name log-aggregator-svc, deployed to default. Specifications include labeled env=staging, with service type NodePort, and proxying to port 6379 on the backend."
296,"Please configure a Deployment identified as analytics-engine within production. Make sure it has based on the mysql:14 image, capping CPU at 200m, having 5 replicated pods, while also with its container called app, and with a CPU request of 200m."
297,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name circuit-breaker, deployed to data. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Specifications include serving on container port 80, with RollingUpdate as the strategy type, pulling golang:latest, running 3 copies, whose container is called worker."
298,The ssl-terminator-svc Service operates in the production namespace. It is configured with as a NodePort service. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It requires the env label set to staging.
299,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as email-sender-config within development. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Make sure it has mapping app_name to user-service, and containing app_port set to 5000."
